source.name: NYC Commuter Cycling Indicator
source.description:
NYC Commuter Cycling Indicator based on counts at selected commuter locations 
The cycling indicator is indexed to Year 2000 = 100
The Commuter Cycling Indicator is an analysis of trends in cycling that makes use of the most robust data available to estimate changes in commuter cycling levels over time. The Commuter Cycling Indicator is not an estimate of the total number of cyclists in New York City.
